                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Boule d'eau"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 3 pts de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">DGT Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> et inflige un </span><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">éclat de miroir</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> d'eau au personnage choisi.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Éclat de miroir d'eau</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT Hydro subis par le personnage affecté +1.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Durée en manches :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">(un seul de ces états peut exister à la fois dans un même camp)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/02/35653081/2b72995c4a7d257472864199056edd68_8214896749517666094.png",
                "id": "talent77474",
                "key": "Explosion d'afflux",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Explosion d'afflux"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 5 pts de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">DGT Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/02/35653081/57d2f05c0e87c6021cd6e4bfb5b031c1_1603261857401650937.png",
                "id": "talent41438",
                "key": "Réflexion ondulée",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Réflexion ondulée"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Hydro et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Évaporation : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Électrocution :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> DGT actuels +1 et inflige 1 pt de DGT de perforation à tous les personnages adverses autre que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Gel :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> DGT actuels +1 et immobilise la cible pendant la manche actuelle (Peut être annulé en avance subissant des DGT physiques ou Pyro, mais DGT +2)</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Fleurissement :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> DGT actuels +1 et crée un</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">noyau Dendro</span> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">qui augmente le prochain coup de DGT Pyro/Électro de 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/02/35653081/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_4226663168157589860.png",
                "id": "talent57886",
                "key": "DGT Hydro",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Hydro"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Durée en manches</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">À chaque fin de manche, </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">durée en manches </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">-1.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois la </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">durée en manches </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisée.</span></p>",
